arts.ttl: Paris Saint-Germain 3-0 Reims: Highlights, man of the match, stats as Barcola, Doue shine in dominant Coupe de France final
arts.sum: Bradley Barcola was on the target as Luis Enrique's Paris Saint-Germain earned their 16th Coupe de France title with a 3-0 win over Reims at Stade de France on Saturday.
